name: YogLabs Warehouse Rush
description:
It's your first day at your new job at the yoglabs warehouse and you've shown up late.

Lucky for you the bosses are out on business so you've got a little time to try and get as many packages loaded as possible. Using your standard issue YogLabs grav-gun you will manipulate physics in order to climb, and collect the hidden presents scattered throughout the warehouse.

Bigger presents are worth more points so keep an eye out.

All assets, code, sound effects and textures were produced by myself par the music.

Music from https://filmmusic.io "Big Rock" by Kevin MacLeod
